<h3 id="2-to-5-player-multiplayer">2 to 5 Player Multiplayer:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Eliminate your friends to take control of the solar system</li>
  <li>Defeated players automatically join another team so everyone stays in the action</li>
  <li>Unlock different Gods with unique powers, but be careful as friends who defeat you will gain them as well</li>
  <li>Add intelligent bots to make the battle even crazier</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="single-player-campaign-beta">Single Player Campaign (BETA):</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Take over the galaxy, one solar system at a time</li>
  <li>Absorb defeated enemies to unlock new Gods with game-changing powers</li>
  <li>Hone your skills on a variety of unique scenarios</li>
</ul>

